trigger a flow at regular intervals. For example, to periodically call an api to retrieve its current state.
Use an Inject node configured to repeat at the desired interval.
The "Inject" node can be configured to repeat at a fixed interval. If desired, it can also be constrained to do so between certain times on certain days

